Minimalistic style: A sleek, clean composition featuring a single glowing digital envelope hovering above an abstract representation of a small island city-state at dusk. The envelope emanates soft concentric rings of light in Singapore's national colors of red and white. Below, geometric shapes suggest modern architecture and infrastructure converging toward a central point. The background transitions from deep navy to warm amber, suggesting the bridge between traditional government and digital future. The envelope casts a gentle shadow that forms the silhouette of interconnected pathways, symbolizing unified citizen services. Empty space dominates the upper portion, creating visual breathing room while maintaining focus on the central motif of secure, streamlined communication.
